
## Building the Electron App

Before building the PKGBUILD, make sure your Electron app source is ready:

```bash
# Directory structure for the app
stormos-welcome-2.0.0/
├── main.js
├── preload.js
├── renderer.js
├── styles.css
├── index.html
├── package.json
├── build/
│   └── icon.png
└── node_modules/
